<br>
The only time a camp designates mob property is when a specific group is camping at a named spawn for a quest or loot. Then usually that 'camp' is respected. Unless this is the case and especially in POV mobs are for the most part FFA.<br>
<br>
Oh and please if your camping east wall and mobs follow normal pathing to the zoneline STFU in ooc about being trained if your group can't handle it then don't camp there. <br>
